ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 16th day of October, 2012, the Order of the Commonwealth Court is AFFIRMED. Appellant’s Motions for Sanctions and for Correction of the Record are DENIED. Appellant’s Motion for Oral Argument is DENIED AS MOOT.
